        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/261">Conradus</persName> dei gratia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Quia ecclesiasticis institutis proficimus, merito
                        ecclesiasticis profectibus insistimus. Cunctis igitur deo nobisque nunc et
                        in posterum militantibus pateat, nos pro nostrae animae futura
                        recompensatione et nostrae consortis <rs key="#Queen">reginae</rs>
                        <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/262">Gisllae</persName> petitoria
                        interventione iuxta nostrae concessionis auctoritatem premissam <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/406">sancte <placeName
                                key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/245">Nouariensis</placeName>
                            ecclesie</orgName>, ubi sanctum Gaudentii corpus humatum requiescit,
                            <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/411">sancti
                            Felicis</orgName> videlicet que vulgo dicitur Regine <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">abbatiam</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName> sitam cum
                        pertinentiis suis -- et habeat potestatem <persName ref="#people/530"
                            key="#Bishops">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> suique successores inibi <rs
                            key="#Abbesses">abbatissam</rs> ordinandi -- presentis paginae nostrae
                        iussionis litteris annotatae testimonio et auctoritate concessisse. <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">Concedimus</rs> itaque <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/327"><placeName
                                key="#Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                                ref="#places/733">Plumbia</placeName></geogName> et alium de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/92"><placeName
                                key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                                ref="#places/54">Oxula</placeName></geogName> cum sua i[nt]egritate
                        et <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/402"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/835">Grauidona</placeName></geogName> cum corte de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/403"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/838">Uespolate</placeName></geogName> cum utrisque
                        portionibus Huberti atque Hugonis et <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs> de
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/839">Uuilingo</placeName> et de <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/840">Cureio</placeName> cum pertinentiis eorum et duos <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/842">Garbania</placeName>, et quicquid <persName><name
                                ref="Hubertus Novarie">Hubertus</name></persName> Nouarie habet
                        intus et de foris, et corticellam que constat in <persName><name
                                ref="Matteus">Matteo</name></persName>, et quicquid tenet in
                            <placeName>Alisade</placeName> et in <placeName ref="#places/841"
                            key="#Property_of_criminals/political_traitors">Crescia</placeName> et
                        in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/843">Xuno</placeName>, et quicquid habet <persName><name
                                ref="Ribaldus">Ribaldus</name></persName> in eodem loco et in
                        Belingo, et quicquid habet <persName><name ref="Hugo">Hugo</name></persName>
                        filius quondam Uualonis in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/736">Pernate</placeName> et in Terdublate cum suis
                        adiacentiis, et <rs key="#Curtes">corticellam</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Redistributive #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/521"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                                ref="#estates/275">Caualli</geogName></placeName> regis, quam tenet
                                <persName><name ref="Richardus">Richardus</name></persName>, cum
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/844">alpe de Otro</placeName>, simul etiam cum
                            <rs>ponte</rs> de <placeName key="#Confiscation" ref="#places/846"
                            >Uarade</placeName>, et roccam Huberti de valle
                            <placeName>Sesedana</placeName> et omnia predia, que ipse retinet in
                        predicta valle et in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/847">Seticiano</placeName>, et quartam portionem de <rs
                            key="#Curtes">corte</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/845"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                                ref="#estates/404">Cerro</geogName></placeName>, et quicquid
                            <persName>Richardus</persName> et <persName>Hubertus</persName> retinent
                        in valle Oxula et circa <rs key="#Lakes">lacum</rs><placeName key="#Lakes"
                            ref="#places/836"> sancti Iulii</placeName> in circuitu, eo videlicet
                        ordine quatinus Petrus pontifex presens eiusdem ecclesiae previsor et cuncti
                        pro tempore ibi locandi predictam sancti Felicis abbatiam que vulgo Regine
                        dicitur et d[uo]s comitatus superius prefatos cum <rs key="#Teloneum"
                            >teloneis</rs> et <rs key="#Districtio">publicis omnibus functionibus
                            regiae potestatis</rs> et p[re]scriptas cortes cum castris earum et
                        simul cum vallibus et ponte ac alpe et mansos superius relatos cum <rs
                            key="#Slave">servis</rs> et utriusque sexus familiis et omnem
                        possessionem Huberti et Richardi circa lacum sancti Iulii habentium earumque
                        pertinentiis et adiacentiis habeant teneant firmiterque possideant;
                        habeantque licentiam legali seu duellari diffinitione emersuras contentiones
                        dirimere, nostra nostrorumque successorum et totius dignitatis seu officii
                        hominum contradictione remota. Si quis igitur huius nostrae corroborationis
                        statuto contraire temptaverit, centum talentorum reus existat, medietatem
                        nobis et alteram eidem ecclesiae persolvenda. Et ut verius credatur, nostro
                        sigillo iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Chuonradi serenissimi (M.) et
                        invictissimi regis. <persName><name ref="Hugo cancellarius"
                            >Hugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem domni
                                <persName><name>Heribonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovit. (SI. D.) Data IIII. id. iunii,
                        indictione VIII, anno incarnationis domini MoXXV, domni vero Chuonradi regis
                        I; acta <placeName ref="#places/4424">Constantie</placeName>; feliciter. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
